e"}}]}]}'), '$.content_html', '<h2 id="turkiyede-mooc-nedir" class="wp-block-heading">What are MOOCs in Turkey?</h2>
<p class="wp-block-paragraph">MOOC stands for Massive Open Online Courses. These types of courses allow participants from all over the world to access education on various subjects via the internet. In Turkey, many universities and educational institutions offer a variety of courses to students through MOOC platforms. These courses are generally free and provide participants with a flexible learning experience.</p>
<p class="wp-block-paragraph">For example, the <a href="https://boenstitu.com/online-egitimler/liderlik" target="_blank" rel="noopener">&#8220;Entrepreneurship&#8221; MOOC offered by Boğaziçi University</a> provides participants with information on the processes of starting a business, while also being supported by practical projects. Such courses provide students with practical experience in addition to theoretical knowledge.</p>
<div id="chat-history" class="chat-history-scroll-container">
<div id="dedd2880d3bdaa41" class="conversation-container message-actions-hover-boundary ng-star-inserted">
<div class="response-container ng-tns-c1654037792-23 response-container-with-gpi ng-star-inserted">
