portunities-in-turkey/#webpage"},"inLanguage":"en-US","mainEntityOfPage":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/marie-curie-and-horizon-europe-opportunities-in-turkey/#webpage"}}]}]}'), '$.content_html', '<h2 id="turkiyede-egitim-firsatlari-marie-curie-ve-horizon-europe-projeleri-nedir" class="wp-block-heading">Educational Opportunities in Turkey: What Are the Marie Curie and Horizon Europe Projects?</h2>
<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The Marie Curie and Horizon Europe projects are major research and education programs supported by the European Union. By participating in these projects, Turkey provides access to international education and research opportunities. Marie Curie fellowships offer researchers the chance to gain international experience and advance their careers, while Horizon Europe projects aim to support innovative research.</p>
<h3 class="wp-block-heading">Marie Curie Fellowships</h3>
<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Marie Curie fellowships provide financial support to individuals in higher education and research. These fellowships encourage researchers to gain experience at different institutions across Europe and develop collaborations. Universities in Turkey benefit from these fellowships by participating in international projects and increasing their research capacity.</p>
<h3 class="wp-block-heading">Horizon Europe Projects</h3>
<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Horizon Europe is the European Union&#8217;s research and innovation program. Turkey participates in many projects within this program, developing international collaborations. These projects aim to produce innovative solutions, particularly in the fields of science, technology, and engineering. Through Horizon Europe projects, universities and research institutions in Turkey are becoming globally competitive.</p>
<p class="wp-block-paragraph">You might also find our article on <a title="ORCID and Researcher IDs in Turkey" href="https://https://roadtostudy.com//turkiyede-orcid-arastirmaci-kimlikleri/">ORCID and Researcher IDs in Turkey</a> helpful.</p>
<h3 id="ufuk-avrupa-projesi-nedir" class="wp-block-heading">What is the Horizon Europe Project?</h3>
<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Horizon Europe is the European Union&#8217;s research and innovation program for the 2021-2027 period. While promoting scientific excellence, this program aims to develop innovative solutions to address societal challenges. By participating in Horizon Europe projects, Turkey has the opportunity to integrate into international research networks. These projects enhance the international recognition of universities and research institutions and contribute to Turkey&#8217;s scientific research.</p>
<h3>Marie Sklodowska-Curie Actions (MSCA) – Horizon Europe Programme</h3>
<p>Marie Sklodowska-Curie Actions (MSCA) is a prestigious research and education support program conducted under the <a href="https://ufukavrupa.org.tr/tr/alanlar-kumeler/marie-sklodowska-curie-alani-tum-cagrilar" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>Horizon Europe</strong></a> programme. Its goal is to offer researchers <strong>international and interdisciplinary research experience</strong>, <strong>career development opportunities</strong>, and <strong>knowledge-sharing possibilities</strong>.</p>
<h4>1. MSCA Doctoral Networks</h4>
<ul>
<li>
<p><strong>Purpose:</strong> To offer researchers postgraduate training and doctoral opportunities, and to support international collaboration.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>Application Deadline:</strong> 25 November 2025</p>
</li>
</ul>
<h4>2. MSCA Postdoctoral Fellowships</h4>
<ul>
<li>
<p><strong>Purpose:</strong> To provide <a href="https://rea.ec.europa.eu/select-language?destination=/node/11" target="_blank" rel="noopener">postdoctoral researchers</a> with career development and international research experience.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>Application Deadline:</strong> 10 September 2025</p>
</li>
</ul>
<h4>3. MSCA &amp; Citizens Programme</h4>
<ul>
<li>
<p><strong>Purpose:</strong> To share research results with the public, and support science communication and awareness projects.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>2023 Call:</strong> 20 June 2023 – 25 October 2023</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p class="wp-block-paragraph">You can also take a look at our article on <a title="Fulbright and Other Academic Exchange Programs in Turkey" href="https://https://roadtostudy.com//turkiyede-fulbright-akademik-degisimi/" data-wplink-url-error="true">Fulbright and Other Academic Exchange Programs in Turkey</a>.</p>
<h2 id="horizon-europe-projeleri-turkiyedeki-uluslararasi-ogrenciler-icin-yeni-imkanlar" class="wp-block-heading">Horizon Europe Projects: New Opportunities for International Students in Turkey</h2>
<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Horizon Europe projects offer various opportunities for international students in Turkey. These projects provide students with the chance to participate in internships, research, and training programs, while also allowing them to gain international experience. Through these projects, universities in Turkey enrich students&#8217; academic lives by offering scholarships and support programs.</p>
<h3 class="wp-block-heading">Example Projects and Opportunities</h3>
<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong>Research Internships:</strong> Students can participate in various research internships as part of Horizon Europe projects. These internships help students develop their academic and professional skills.</li>
<li><strong>Scholarship Programs:</strong> Universities in Turkey offer scholarships within the framework of Horizon Europe projects, helping international students cover their educational expenses.</li>
<li><strong>International Collaborations:</strong> Through these projects, students have the opportunity to join international research teams and collaborate with people from different cultures.</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="marie-curie-ve-horizon-europe-turkiyedeki-egitim-yolculugunuzda-nasil-destek-olur" class="wp-block-heading">Marie Curie and Horizon Europe: How They Can Support Your Educational Journey in Turkey</h2>
<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The Marie Curie and Horizon Europe projects offer significant support for your educational journey in Turkey. These projects enable students to gain international experience and advance their academic careers. By collaborating on these projects, universities in Turkey provide students with a variety of educational opportunities.</p>
<h3 class="wp-block-heading">Educational Support Programs</h3>
<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong>Research Opportunities:</strong> Marie Curie and Horizon Europe projects support students&#8217; academic careers by offering them research opportunities.</li>
<li><strong>Mentorship Programs:</strong> Within these projects, experienced academics provide mentorship to students. This allows students to receive support in setting and navigating their career goals.</li>
<li><strong>Networking:</strong> International projects offer students the chance to meet and collaborate with researchers from different countries. This helps students expand their professional networks.</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="marie-curie-bursu-ne-kadar" class="wp-block-heading">How Much is the Marie Curie Fellowship?</h2>
<div class="wDYxhc" lang="tr-TR" data-md="61">
<div class="c7twPc">
<div class="LGOjhe" data-attrid="wa:/description" data-hveid="CBsQAA">
<ul data-start="45" data-end="349">
<li data-start="45" data-end="143">
<p data-start="47" data-end="143"><strong data-start="47" data-end="64">Monthly Support:</strong> Since 2020, MSCA fellowships can be <strong data-start="98" data-end="124">up to €4,880 per month</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="144" data-end="259">
<p data-start="146" data-end="259"><strong data-start="146" data-end="157">Coverage:</strong> The fellowship is designed to cover living expenses, travel support, and research costs.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="260" data-end="349">
<p data-start="262" data-end="349"><strong data-start="262" data-end="271">Purpose:</strong> To provide researchers with international experience and to support their careers.</p>
</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
